  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_introduction.header": "Accessing Items",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_introduction.text_1": "Right-click the Pressing Tub with an itemStack to store it\nNote: The Pressing Tub can only hold one type of item at a time.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_introduction.text_2": "Right-click the Pressing Tub with an empty hand to take out 1 item.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_introduction.text_3": "Sneak + right-click the Pressing Tub with an empty hand to take out all items.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_pressing.header": "Pressing Juice",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_pressing.text_1": "Place pressable ingredients into the Pressing Tub.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_pressing.text_2": "Jump and jump on the Pressing Tub to gradually press the ingredients into juice.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_pressing.text_3": "However, if the item inside the Pressing Tub cannot be pressed, it will be scattered by the jumping.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_variant.header": "Angled Variant",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_variant.text_1": "Placing a Pressing Tub against a wall creates an angled variant.\nAngled Pressing Tubs can still store items normally.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_variant.text_2": "However, angled Pressing Tubs cannot be used for pressing juice.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.pressing_tub_variant.text_3": "Similarly, their contents will not be scattered by jumping.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.header": "Using the Barrel",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_1": "First, open the lid.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_2": "Then, add the fluid and any required ingredients.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_3": "Once everything is ready, close the lid.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_4": "Now, simply wait patiently for the wine to brew.\nThe longer it brews, the higher the quality of the wine.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_5": "Right-click the barrel to check the brewing progress.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.barrel_introduction.text_6": "Place a Glass Bottle under the tap and right-click it to bottle the finished wine.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.header": "Wild Generation",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_1": "Explore around, and you can find these Grapevines on trees in the wild.\nSimilar to bee nests, using Bone Meal on a tree sapling near flowers also has a chance to generate Grapevines.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_2": "No tools are needed, break them with an empty hand to obtain Grapevines.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_3": "Grapevines can be planted under full blocks and leave blocks.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_4": "Grapevines planted this way will grow downwards but will not bear grapes.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_wild_generation.text_5": "Use Shears to prune a Grapevine, stopping its downward growth.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.header": "Planting Grapes",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_1": "Plant a Grapevine on a Trellis placed one block above the soil.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_2": "The Grapevine will prioritize growing onto the Trellis above it.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_3": "Then, it will spread horizontally to surrounding Trellises.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_4": "When a Trellis with a Grapevine has an empty space below it, it will begin to bear grapes.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_5": "Once the grapes are ripe, harvesting them with an empty hand yields 1-2 grapes.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.grapevine_planting.text_6": "Harvesting with Shears yields 2-3 grapes.",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.tag.brewing" : "Brewing",
  "kaleidoscope_tavern.ponder.tag.brewing.description" : "Everything you need to know to start brewing from scratch."
}
